    </omtext><omtext class="comment">
      <CMP> Positions of primes in A033491. [From _R. J. Mathar_, Nov 01 2010]</CMP>
    </omtext><omtext class="reference">
      <CMP> R. K. Guy, &quot;Collatz's Sequence&quot; in Unsolved Problems in Number Theory, 2nd ed. New York: Springer-Verlag, pp. 215-218, 1994</CMP>
